items.headline: The Tiny Monsters Wiki
items.desc: Tiny Monsters Wiki is a collaborative database about the Tiny Monsters game developed by TinyCo. The objective of the game is to collect, feed, and breed rare and unusual monsters, who are categorized into different fields such as fire, water, and and electric. There are new monsters and decorations added all the time!
